== Game play ==

With the optional Microdeal 4 player adaptor, the game allowed 4 players to play (3 against the computer, or 2 against 2).<ref>[http://www.gamefaqs.com/amiga/928042-amiga-soccer Entry] at Gamefaqs</ref>

